snippet: Clint Dempsey’s goal gave the United States a 1-0 victory over Honduras in Miami, and delivered the team’s first win in five games under Coach Jurgen Klinsmann.
lead_paragraph: Clint Dempsey’s goal gave the United States a 1-0 victory over Honduras in Miami, and delivered the team’s first win in five games under Coach Jurgen Klinsmann.
